for big families. Save more annually!", "desc_hi": "बड़े परिवारों के लिए सबसे अच्छा मूल्य। सालाना अधिक बचत करें!", "category": "Yearly Family Packs", "is_best_value": true, "discount": "20% OFF", "original_price": "18000.00", "unit": "Yearly", "frequency_en": "Monthly", "frequency_hi": "मासिक", "slot_en": "Morning", "slot_hi": "सुबह", "status_en": "Active", "status_hi": "सक्रिय", "product": 1, "quantity_litres": 1, "frequency": "yearly", "slot": "morning", "status": "active", "created_at": "2026-02-27T18:00:51.408Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-15T09:32:24.806Z", "total_amount": "15000.00"}}, {"model": "subscriptions.subscription", "pk": 8, "fields": {"image": null, "plan_name_en": "Daily Fresh Trial", "plan_name_hi": "दैनिक ताजा ट्रायल", "desc_en": "One week trial of fresh milk", "desc_hi": "ताजा दूध का एक सप्ताह का परीक्षण", "category": "Monthly Essentials", "is_best_value": false, "discount": null, "original_price": "350.00", "unit": "Weekly", "frequency_en": "Monthly", "frequency_hi": "मासिक", "slot_en": "Morning", "slot_hi": "सुबह", "status_en": "Active", "status_hi": "सक्रिय", "product": 1, "quantity_litres": 1, "frequency": "monthly", "slot": "morning", "status": "active", "created_at": "2026-02-27T18:00:51.414Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-15T09:33:25.515Z", "total_amount": "300.00"}}, {"model": "support.faq", "pk": 2, "fields": {"question_en": "How to change delivery time?", "question_hi": "डिलीवरी का समय कैसे बदलें?", "answer_en": "To change your delivery time, go to 'Daily Milk Schedule' or 'Active Subscriptions', select your plan, and update the delivery slot (Morning/Evening) as per your preference.", "answer_hi": "अपने डिलीवरी समय को बदलने के लिए, 'डेली मिल्क शेड्यूल' या 'एक्टिव सब्सक्रिप्शन' पर जाएं, अपना प्लान चुनें और अपनी पसंद के अनुसार डिलीवरी स्लॉट (सुबह/शाम) अपडेट करें।", "created_at": "2026-02-27T17:15:33.934Z"}}, {"model": "support.faq", "pk": 3, "fields": {"question_en": "Payment methods accepted?", "question_hi": "भुगतान के तरीके स्वीकार किए गए?", "answer_en": "We accept all major credit/debit cards, UPI, and digital wallets like PhonePe, Paytm, and Google Pay. You can manage your default payment method in the 'Payments' section.", "answer_hi": "हम सभी प्रमुख क्रेडिट/डेबिट कार्ड, यूपीआई और PhonePe, Paytm और Google Pay जैसे डिजिटल वॉलेट स्वीकार करते हैं। आप 'भुगतान' अनुभाग में अपनी डिफ़ॉल्ट भुगतान विधि प्रबंधित कर सकते हैं।", "created_at": "2026-02-27T17:17:35.879Z"}}, {"model": "support.faq", "pk": 4, "fields": {"question_en": "How to pause subscription?", "question_hi": "सदस्यता को कैसे रोकें?", "answer_en": "You can pause your subscription anytime from the 'Active Subscriptions' screen. Select the plan you wish to pause and toggle the 'Pause' button. You won't be charged for the paused days.", "answer_hi": "आप 'सक्रिय सदस्यताएँ' स्क्रीन से अपनी सदस्यता को कभी भी रोक सकते हैं। जिस प्लान को आप रोकना चाहते हैं उसे चुनें और 'रोकें' बटन को दबाएँ। रोके गए दिनों के लिए आपसे कोई शुल्क नहीं लिया जाएगा।", "created_at": "2026-02-27T17:19:32.760Z"}}, {"model": "support.faq", "pk": 5, "fields": {"question_en": "What is the quality of milk?", "question_hi": "दूध की गुणवत्ता कैसी है?", "answer_en": "Our milk is sourced directly from certified organic farms, tested for over 20+ purity parameters, and delivered fresh within hours of milking.", "answer_hi": "हमारा दूध सीधे प्रमाणित जैविक फार्मों से प्राप्त किया जाता है, 20 से अधिक शुद्धता मानकों पर परखा जाता है, और दुहने के कुछ ही घंटों के भीतर ताजा वितरित किया जाता है।", "created_at": "2026-02-27T17:21:04.686Z"}}, {"model": "support.faq", "pk": 6, "fields": {"question_en": "Can I order extra items daily?", "question_hi": "क्या मैं प्रतिदिन अतिरिक्त सामान ऑर्डर कर सकता हूँ?", "answer_en": "Yes! You can add one-time items to your next morning's delivery by browsing our products and adding them to the cart before the cut-off time (usually 11:00 PM).", "answer_hi": "जी हां! आप हमारे उत्पादों को ब्राउज़ करके और कट-ऑफ समय (आमतौर पर रात 11:00 बजे) से पहले उन्हें कार्ट में जोड़कर अगली सुबह की डिलीवरी में एक बार की वस्तुएं शामिल कर सकते हैं।", "created_at": "2026-02-27T17:23:12.948Z"}}, {"model": "support.supportmessage", "pk": 1, "fields": {"user": null, "name": "arkan", "phone": "33", "message": "Product is not found", "is_resolved": true, "created_at": "2026-02-26T06:16:43.510Z"}}, {"model": "users.user", "pk": 30, "fields": {"password": "pbkdf2_sha256$1000000$9GgIoSxUPL9wRsCMaszqsS$L7jHPm5dxRkWggJoQ7ot2FBQlJ+wsVuNV+eizngjF9M=", "last_login": "2026-03-26T05:16:40.821Z", "is_superuser": true, "is_staff": true, "is_active": true, "date_joined": "2026-03-26T05:15:54.161Z", "email": "arkannshaikh07@gmail.com", "user_id": null, "full_name": "", "role": "customer", "phone": null, "profile_image": "", "push_token": null, "groups": [], "user_permissions": []}}, {"model": "users.user", "pk": 31, "fields": {"password": "pbkdf2_sha256$1000000$RNRDwMuHz2ozeWHwevP3NO$Bv50pLxcHLIrrhb3mi4PF9v97860NIJrJPRZVa4JRDI=", "last_login": "2026-03-29T11:36:35.881Z", "is_superuser": false, "is_staff": false, "is_active": true, "date_joined": "2026-03-26T06:43:41.242Z", "email": "1234567890@noemail.local", "user_id": "CUST-2026-4326", "full_name": "Arkan Shaikh", "role": "customer", "phone": "1234567890", "profile_image": "", "push_token": null, "groups": [], "user_permissions": []}}, {"model": "users.user", "pk": 32, "fields": {"password": "pbkdf2_sha256$1000000$bJuFyKnFTNDNMBgHWxQCSz$3uigrLIhMszo+ac/kwr9EhiTewzoJUW8OmnnRqG+o9w=", "last_login": "2026-03-28T21:41:23.850Z", "is_superuser": false, "is_staff": false, "is_active": true, "date_joined": "2026-03-26T07:28:04.997Z", "email": "arkansshaikh07@gmail.com", "user_id": "VEN-2026-9109", "full_name": "Arkan Shaikh", "role": "vendor", "phone": "9876543210", "profile_image": "", "push_token": null, "groups": [], "user_permissions": []}}, {"model": "users.customer", "pk": 1, "fields": {"cust_id": "CUST-2026-4326", "name": "Arkan Shaikh", "email": null, "phone": "1234567890", "password": "arkan07", "otp_code": "1234", "ot